{"tid":1688681,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你班mon po狗仲自認係白警 點解要剝削被捕者嘅權利?","createTime":"2019-11-02T13:55:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-04T01:29:45.000Z","uid":225100,"like":31,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"bffff22b707013a9679ac702476e5213e1c5265e","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:55:12.000Z","msg":"如果你班mon po狗仲自認係白警<br />\n仲<span style=\"color: red;\">自覺係正義</span><br />\n點解要剝削被捕者嘅權利?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hate.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點解唔畀佢哋見律師聯絡家人?<br />\n點解要千方百計拖延唔畀佢哋及早去醫院驗傷?<br />\n點解要侮辱佢哋?<br />\n點解要非禮女被捕人?<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">點解唔保障被捕人嘅權利?</span><br />\n<br />\n你哋唔係好<span style=\"color: red;\">專業</span>架咩<br />\n退十億步 我當現場電光火石<br />\n但返到警署呢 個個都任你哋魚肉<br />\n明明伸張緊正義<br />\n點解你哋要返警署打人?點解你哋要返警署先犯法?程序 警察通例 法例點寫?<br />\n<br />\n你哋再唔揸正黎做<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">就真係中晒黑衣人嘅計啦</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n越剝削只會越證明<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">你哋個個都係黑警 冇一個無辜</span>呢件事係啱<br />\n<br />\n你哋咪繼續睇藍絲5毛page打飛機lor<br />\n繼續當我哋係收錢做野<br />\n繼續當自己係正義lor<br />\n<br />\n等有一日中共贏咗<br />\n<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">千山盡 良弓藏<br />\n狡兔死 <span style=\"color: red;\">走狗烹</span></span></blockquote><br />\n唔識就自己google下<br />\n<br />\n仲以為老解武警同志黎香港係幫你哋?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">中共驚有日成立獨立調查委員會時你哋叛變阿傻閪</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">你哋唯一可以自保嘅方法<br />\n就係保留所有證據<br />\n包括上司嘅犯罪證據同埋你自己揸正黎做 清白嘅證據</span></span><br />\n然後祈求香港人嬴<br />\n<br />\n因為我哋香港人把口就講死全家<br />\n但實際上係一個好重視真相嘅民族<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">只要真相係你哋白警唔犯法揸正黎做<br />\n又願意指正其他黑警<br />\n我哋香港人一定會揸正黎做</span><br />\n<br />\n當大sir搞緊移民<br />\n你哋班藍衫唔想做condom嘅話<br />\n自己用下個腦諗下應該點做<br />\n下下唔做兩手準備<br />\n到輸到一敗塗地嘅時候<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">後悔就太遲了</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<code>不畏懼 不徇私 不對他人懷惡意</code>"},{"pid":"59949a91856af60c2bf610f0e19d571379a7d9c7","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:55:51.000Z","msg":"曱甴王 甴近平 江甴文 毛甴東 習曱甴"},{"pid":"e75bf6c452954a0227d2d01266c4fd0b86684b5b","tid":1688681,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=9294be0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},{"pid":"bd04d029fc704731dabaf21b20e93a8e0ea98bbf","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:56:56.000Z","msg":"保障被捕人應有的權益<br />\n定係繼續做黑警 自己揀"},{"pid":"2a4d41fbda04104245c714c9422590a03630aac2","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e75bf6c452954a0227d2d01266c4fd0b86684b5b","tid":1688681,"uid":249263,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:55:54.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n幫手retweet<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">入 /task3</span></span><br />\n燒背 候選人被捕 消防員被警察毆打<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FTwitterHelpBot&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RH8q8VOs0%2BPBwwlvB7nX800%3D&h=9294be0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/TwitterHelpBot</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:58:06.000Z","msg":"done<br />\n<br />\n曱甴王 甴近平 江甴文 毛甴東 習曱甴"},{"pid":"9067011c50b65cc94991ebafba079606599b8baf","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:59:01.000Z","msg":"mon post 9中晒計<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05b7bfce5f962ad5cfa692ed1bf7680ee039b837","tid":1688681,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"仲邊有白警"},{"pid":"e9ab61e9364a2c80b6930b5aa0750eedbf8cbcf0","tid":1688681,"uid":259329,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:01:13.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"458270a48f914f7a0d319130f485c08e0538fd3f","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:04:22.000Z","msg":"個個星期都拉幾百個<br />\n以為自己贏硬?<br />\n邊一邊贏 你班黑警都係輸<br />\n中共只會成立ICoI 放棄你哋<br />\n但香港人贏 你班一時良心發現嘅警察可能會有一線生機<br />\n<br />\n自己諗"},{"pid":"9973188007a31dfe594ae0994d98cc309dcd6c9d","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"05b7bfce5f962ad5cfa692ed1bf7680ee039b837","tid":1688681,"uid":55955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T13:59:51.000Z","msg":"仲邊有白警"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"但仲有聰明嘅黑警<br />\n做人唔做兩手準備<br />\n好易輸到一敗塗地"},{"pid":"204a822fb45e9f370475c448c269dc0b07eb45f3","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:06:05.000Z","msg":"千山盡 良弓藏<br />\n狡兔死 走狗烹"},{"pid":"7deb7c4c4fdfd57a5d6609dc2fe1db1cbdc53c02","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:06:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"306f99a9e07058e07724321927f970b400906b1f","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:14:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63b445af7fedea69fa675d3b8924f491c10e35f5","tid":1688681,"uid":25825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T14:21:29.000Z","msg":"曱甴王 甴近平 江甴文 毛甴東 習曱甴"},{"pid":"162fd7d2861aac45bcf92d11cd67bfc3397193e4","tid":1688681,"uid":225100,"like